Weighted Chinese Plank
Set-up: 
Place two benches approximately 3-4ft apart.
Lay feet on one bench and shoulders on the other bench.
Put the toes, legs and glutes together. 

Execution: 
Push through the toes and hands to a plank position with straight arms. 
Place a weight on the back. 
Keep the quads, glutes and belly contracted. 
Hold for the desired time.
